---

<section id="story" class="section story-bg">
	<div class="container">
		<div style="text-align: center; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
			<h2 class="section-title fade-in-up">The Coach Behind the Results</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="grid-2 story-content fade-in-up delay-100">
			
			<div class="story-image-wrap">
				<img src="/coach.jpg" alt="Salakawy Coach" class="story-image" loading="lazy" />
			</div>
			
			<div class="story-text">
				<h3>Turning Fitness into a Lifestyle</h3>
				<p>
					Since 2021, I've helped <strong>over 7,000 people</strong> transform their bodies and health. 
					My mission is to show everyone that proper nutrition does not mean starving yourself or eating boring food.
				</p>
				<p>
					I've worked with clients as young as 8 years old and up to 71. 
					I've guided people through some of the toughest cases, including <strong>PCOS, insulin resistance, type 1 & 2 diabetes, and even cancer.</strong>
				</p>
				<p>
					No matter your age, condition, or schedule, I tailor the perfect flexible diet plan that ensures you actually enjoy the process. 
					A diet plan you can get anywhere, but what I offer is a real transformation mindset.
				</p>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.story-bg {
		background-color: var(--surface-color);
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
	}

	.story-content {
		align-items: center;
		gap: 4rem;
	}

	.story-image-wrap {
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		overflow: hidden;
		position: relative;
	}

	.story-image-wrap::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
		box-shadow: inset 0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
		z-index: 1;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.story-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
		filter: brightness(0.9) contrast(1.1);
		transition: transform var(--transition);
	}

	.story-image-wrap:hover .story-image {
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}

	.story-text h3 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--accent-color);
	}

	.story-text p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.story-text p strong {
		color: var(--text-main);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.story-content {
			gap: 2rem;
		}
		.story-text h3 {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .story-text p {
            text-align: center;
        }
	}
</style>
